Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:03.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一眼就能明白吧  在做餃子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  不覺得做的很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:13.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,皺褶很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說  離截稿日期不是只剩六小時了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好啦  你也來做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個是不是很完美？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:36.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是傳說中的截稿期前的逃避現實麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.43,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H373745&\pos(742,794)}截稿期前的逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有時  被逼上絕路的漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會突然的開始改變房間的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或者突然開始做起豪華大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及開始打掃平時絕對不會管的換氣扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,此外  可能是因為罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比起像遊戲以及娛樂用的活動  大多都是家務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好了  幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不煎一下麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:04.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,煎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種事在原稿完成後也能做吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總算趕上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如說  要是不做餃子會更從容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因為做了餃子才趕上的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這門外漢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂啊
