Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸做的咖哩甜甜的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸後天就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以帶姬去想去的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後天我要去臨海學校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.90,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H51545F&\1a&H0D&\frz25.75\move(471.2,636.4,560,644)}臨海學校的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一個月之前就發了通知單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,過  過去要多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們會去游泳  捉蟲  還有辦篝火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:46.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,捉蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辦篝火？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好擔心  好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去海邊職員旅行還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都到極限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,忘掉漫畫的事情  好好地休整一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天會住在哪兒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從熟人漫畫家那兒借來的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還真肯借出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,多虧了鎌倉病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然今天去的是千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,鎌倉病？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很早之前就得以廣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家為了逃避現實所引發的現象之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:32.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,某個漫畫家疲於每週的截稿日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妄想著有一天能在海邊悠閒地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:42.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後終於他在鎌倉買了工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  從這之後才是恐怖的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為太遠了助手不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,店鋪關門太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為潮氣導致筆尖生鏽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:59.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最後他從夢中驚醒  逃回了東京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:00.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從漫畫家那兒借來多餘的別墅才會如此簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來…如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:12.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都說了別談漫畫的事情了會變陰暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這  這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,結果是被叫過來做清潔麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話就跟截稿日前的逃避現實沒區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  老師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來這兒真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在這兒做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,職員旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,碰巧合宿的地方就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就很在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為  實在太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可愛什麼的  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那當然可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.75,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465,745.2)}在說姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.75,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500.2,748.6)}在說自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這件事請對姬保密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這之後還得帶孩子們去捉獨角仙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,獨角仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.69,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz286.7\pos(1380.8,177.6)\c&H66656E&}起鬨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.69,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz288.5\pos(969.6,243.2)\c&H66656E&}起鬨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是只有姬沒有捉到會不會被欺負？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  我真的可愛麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子君  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去買獨角仙回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,買儘可能大隻的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H486EC8&\3c&HE5E5E7&\pos(880,49.6)}寵物天國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H6D7788&\pos(742.4,601.6)}槌之子進貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  把這個放在姬捉得到的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有誰會買赫克力士大兜蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:41.21,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：赫克力斯大兜蟲是世界上最長的甲蟲，也是全世界最大的甲蟲之一，分布於中南美洲的熱帶雨林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你不說過買儘可能大隻的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小女孩在千葉捉到了這種蟲會上新聞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H454041&\frz13.64\pos(681.6,172.8)}在千葉縣內發現了赫克力士大兜蟲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H444142&\pos(1504,403.2)\frz288.1}臨海學校中的小學生發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H484547&\frz15.6\pos(558.4,920)}被發現的赫克力士大兜蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.43,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)\fs60\c&HF7E1BB&\3c&H231818&\pos(137.6,56)}有赫克力士大兜蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被發現作弊  然後被全國上下批判該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管蟲子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其他的也很令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  又下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒  還是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  因為很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請不要說兩遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:09.19,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord5\c&H5CE8F1&\3c&H2127A3&\pos(257.6,110.4)}臉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提這之後的安排是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我星期天會在家無所事事  空著的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說孩子們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他們在準備晚飯的咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提姬因為要負責調味而幹勁十足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,調味？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz268.9\pos(1795.2,281.6)\c&H90969F&}好難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.7\pos(1297.6,204.8)\c&H90969F&}好難吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&HDFAACA&\3c&H9F8AA7&\pos(1009.6,670.4)}嗚嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,任性的請求不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事  我的兒子是「雞雞復雞雞」的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\i1\c&H474144&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1000,126.4)}現在話題中的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\bord3\frz7.293\3c&H775DBA&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1078.4,278.4)}咖哩店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 8 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz270\c&H494349&\pos(1139.2,440)}香料的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H51526F&\frz25.41\pos(1052.8,852.8)}那美味讓人無法自拔！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad1\frz33.8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H565775&\4c&H525572&\pos(232,401.6)}這個咖哩好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\c&H6E94C2&\frz258.3\pos(1624,518.4)}超越了咖哩的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H6D92C9&\frz348.3\pos(1523.2,798.4)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交給您一定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  來幫忙淘米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那摩斯戴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.11,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：梵語裡的問候語，意為「向你鞠躬致敬」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.77,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H2114EC&\3c&H6DC6EC&\frz11.84\pos(377.6,313.6)}完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:45.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,兩次說我可愛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說後藤老師對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是不行哦  一子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那可是學生的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的哦  後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要攪起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,媽媽沒教過你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  有在好好幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她一直都是那副像是什麼都沒在思考的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺不是什麼都沒思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是有意裝作什麼都沒思考的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起  說了多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是您看  世上不是也有許多思考後也無法改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無可奈何的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,思考後也無法改變的  無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像是母親的事情  以及我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有意裝作沒在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定孩子也在用孩子的方式去逃避現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別說玩了  連食慾都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,筋疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明是來休息的這也太慘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這  這兒又有海又有山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天連同今天的份一起玩個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大海  難得買好了泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在山上燒烤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.22,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HDEA568&\pos(379.2,316.8)}颱風消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.22,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\c&HB1654F&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(939.2,785.6)}「絕型」{\b0}蹂躪關東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太慘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你們多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬她們中止了臨海學校的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,似乎明早就會回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因為颱風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以不要在室內穿泳裝麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行麼  難得買都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這天氣什麼都幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別說大海了  一步都出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,停電？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,手機電池用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:24.56,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}懶懶散散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,電視和遊戲都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,網絡也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已經把放廁所裡的Jump讀了上百遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在的年輕人沒設備連打發時間都不會了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在老師那時代是怎麼打發時間的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如思考木紋最像哪個SMAP成員的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再比如找出最像手的窗簾皺褶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很好玩哦  來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊我已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有什麼東西沒  有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,紙和鉛筆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在畫漫畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們啊  都來別墅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也讓我畫畫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這回超級有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在露營時我做的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:38.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是太辣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然咖哩還是爸爸做的最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個印度廚師究竟是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是有意裝作什麼都沒思考的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有沒有什麼事情想問爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說咖哩是什麼味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咖哩不就是咖哩味的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就猜到是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或許姬是真的什麼事情也沒在想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來了  把原稿藏好了  將漫畫的味道消除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:49.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs70\c&H6C6669&\pos(913.6,145.6)}創發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我公司的解決方案是這樣那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是姬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,技術革新是這樣那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,企業條例又是這樣那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哇  爸爸在工作誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是防災訓練日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:49.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是在避難訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是姬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  讓姬知道我是漫畫家這件事正是最大的災害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(410,74)}不推
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(413.2,362)}不跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(414.8,710.8)}不講話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以這當然就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了應對萬一姬跑到這裡來時的突發情況的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(412.8,68.8)}不放漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(417.6,368)}不畫漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(409.6,672)}不完成漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我會知道就有鬼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師每年可都少不了這個訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來舉行反思會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,筧君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就不能再畫可愛點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反思這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那老師你來畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然無論怎麼畫都比不上真人可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(312,198.4)}不推
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(308.8,409.6)}可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(313.6,627.2)}擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1564.8,683.2)}不放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1484.8,816)}不畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1424,942.4)}不完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  這個很好吃喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要好好吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這份可愛無法用畫筆來表達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了守護這笑容  絕對不能被她發現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我居然在畫那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,急急急急急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院你這傢伙  現在趕快滾過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在可不行哦  我現在在北海道出差…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不記得我同意過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個我也沒同意過  所以沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事個鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你眼前不就是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真沒想到就連「風之緊身褲」這種作品都會有山寨周邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說「就連」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:27.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要還是個編輯的話就去投訴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  那個  關於這些面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一點都不受歡迎  完全賣不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  你完全不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他說完全賣不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,問題不在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有時候會發生這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明並不是很受歡迎的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卻有其山寨周邊充斥在市場上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能是在偶然看到的雜誌上的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其作品又偶然的正是雜誌封面又是刊頭彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就決定是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是誤認為這是一部很受歡迎的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管了  我自己去交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你給我負責  拿著這些東西然後消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,帶著這傢伙和這些面具藏起來  可不要被姬發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好慢哦  你去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來要買什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想吃棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這有棉花糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.70,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}風之緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子君  你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:43.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,搬回去的時候記得可別太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把所有子彈給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:54.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還是沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒中  沒中  沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個面具挺好賣的  明年我要多做10倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要增加5倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明年老師還得把這些東西10倍全部買完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這時候的他還仍未知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這個時候會發出警報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道  姬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,檢測我們訓練成果的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,將漫畫的味道消除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把所有工具收納起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.71,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs70\c&H6C6669&\pos(913.6,145.6)}創發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們是公安警察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們接到一起報案說是有多數非特定的男女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,時常攜帶著大量的食物進行集會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地干著些什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因此懷疑這裡是不是反社會團體的一個據點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從旁人來看確實有些可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請讓我們檢查一下裡邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:55.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼  這用塑料口袋裝著的大量白色粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這並不是白色粉末只是棉花糖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你還沒吃完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也不想想這得有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來這個就是你們組織的資金來源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定電腦裡還有其資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我這就調查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:12.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:13.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
