Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729.6,476.8)}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710.4,539.2)}幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,603.2)}酒會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫姬的面具時所搜索的詞語有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.68,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\fscx83\fscy98\c&H747476&\pos(672,401.6)}可愛的幼女畫法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恐怕會被誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多能請回了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然我不太想說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:36.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們其實是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你覺得會有這樣的漫畫工作室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的好像也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我找到了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,女性緊身褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個是作為資料用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你用來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你問用途？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然是戴在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來是搶劫銀行時用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這次還找到了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然你們是銀行搶劫犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是作為資料用的模型槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.26,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934.4,91.2)\c&H3D3D4C&}使用故事情節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.26,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3D3D48&\pos(492.8,289.6)}主人公緊身褲打出去的球被狙擊槍打上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就連日本刀都有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3C3C49&\pos(1515.2,427.2)}使用故事情節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H3D3D48&\pos(352,177.6)\frz270}使用日本刀在有利位置開洞隨後將球輕推入洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3D3D48&\pos(307.2,177.6)}出自敵人武士安全褲登場一回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那也是作為資料用的模型刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們就是打算用這個襲擊官邸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家們總是會最先買這些東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們已經無法再抵賴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.82,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz267.2\move(1011.2,48,1094,60)}搶劫時用的連褲襪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.82,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz283.7\move(900.8,417.6,995,425)}壁櫃裡隱藏著的白色粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz260.2\move(742.4,392,1140,390)}槍械管制刀具等大量武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz279.6\move(278.4,35.2,700,78)}在空中散布的無人飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們難道企圖推翻這個國家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我現在好像感覺自己真的是反社會團體的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大致上沒什麼錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像我們這樣的組織末端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定在不知不覺中已經參與了犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們自首
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請逮捕我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  你們冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師啊  您可是會有好長一段時間見不到姬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自首吧  讓自己的罪孽減輕一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我承認了  是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  這人真的是個漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,少騙人了  你有什麼東西能夠證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是我的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.45,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H16161D&\pos(828.6,895.8)}作者近照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看了你的全裸照片後  好像放過我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正這東西都已經是出版了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,祭典的那天我好像沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我什麼時候給你買了這樣的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這件別人說是手縫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿給鄰居家的阿姨看後  阿姨告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是爸爸你縫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在壁櫥裡找到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:41.24,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878.4,340.8)\c&H0E0E0E&}10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這件裝在10歲的盒子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其它的箱子你看了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只看到10歲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為我才10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就連16歲的箱子也有  我好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下次縫一件連衣裙給我好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害  爸爸什麼都會縫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那也縫雙鞋子給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,鞋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還要一副眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,眼鏡可不是能縫出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是覺得爸爸的話  應該就能縫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且姬你的眼睛也不是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要的是裝飾的眼鏡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  突然讓我教你怎麼縫紉東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這些你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於還是去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交給她鑰匙的是小羅砂你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可沒這樣的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  真虧能隱瞞到現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟當事人也不打算了解嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父親的隱瞞之事就是作畫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來到鎌倉後  我知曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,同時也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實並不是父親隱瞞著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是我並不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:38.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概  是我害怕去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,知道父親的工作後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不想知道的事情也得被迫知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺我和父親快樂的生活會就此破碎
