Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H898674&\pos(614.4,280)}17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H61605C&\pos(601.6,529.6)}18歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H61605C&\pos(920,278.4)}19歲
